        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>You do not receive the message right after when you open the app. You see the first screen and can choose a category. You receive a message about a connection problem when you try to see the product list.</p>

<p>Reproducibility: <br/>
Always.</p>

<p>Steps to reproduce:<br/>
1. Open Bershka app;<br/>
2. Choose a category from the menu;<br/>
3. Add a product to cart;<br/>
4. Minimize the app. Turn off the Wi-Fi and reopen the app.</p>

<p>Actual result: <br/>
The app is loaded. You see the first screen and can choose a category. You receive a message about a connection problem when you try to see the product list.</p>

<p><span class="error">Can only create thumbnails for attached images</span></p>

<p><span class="error">Can only create thumbnails for attached images</span></p>




<p><span class="error">Can only create thumbnails for attached images</span></p>

<p>Expected result: <br/>
After you open the app you should receive an error message for missing connection. </p>
            <br/>
        </td>
